#ROOM
Vnum     26000
Name     &MShadowglen - Base of Aldrassil&d~
Sector   forest~
Desc     You stand at the base of Aldrassil, a massive, glowing tree nested within
the even larger boughs of Teldrassil. The air here is thick with natural
magic, and the eternal twilight of the Night Elven lands paints the
forest in beautiful shades of violet and silver.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    26001
Desc      The center of the Shadowglen encampment.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction up~
ToRoom    26005
Desc      The high branches of Aldrassil.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 26011 1 26000
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     26001
Name     &MShadowglen - Center&d~
Sector   forest~
Desc     A peaceful, bustling glade where young Night Elves take their first
steps. Trainers offer guidance under the glowing leaves, while initiates
practice their strikes on the woodland creatures wandering nearby.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    26000
Desc      The base of the great tree.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    26003
Desc      A rocky outcropping.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    26004
Desc      A thicket of ancient trees.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    26002
Desc      The northern edge of the glen.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 26010 2 26001
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     26002
Name     &MShadowglen - Northern Edge&d~
Sector   forest~
Desc     The glowing foliage thins out here, revealing the darker, more untamed
woods. Young Nightsabers prowl through the tall grass, practicing their
hunting skills.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    26001
Desc      The center of Shadowglen.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    26008
Desc      A dark, web-filled cave.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 26000 2 26002
  Reset G 1 26000 10
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     26003
Name     &MShadowglen - Eastern Rocks&d~
Sector   hills~
Desc     Small, mischievous Grells dance among these mossy rocks. They are mostly
harmless, though they delight in stealing shiny things from passing
adventurers.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    26001
Desc      The center of Shadowglen.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 26002 2 26003
  Reset G 1 26002 10
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     26004
Name     &MShadowglen - Western Thicket&d~
Sector   forest~
Desc     The trees here are ancient and incredibly thick. Small, peaceful nature
elementals known as Timberlings shuffle through the fallen leaves, tending
to the roots of the forest.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    26001
Desc      The center of Shadowglen.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    26007
Desc      The path leading out of the glen.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 26005 2 26004
  Reset E 1 26004 10 11
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     26005
Name     &MHigh Canopy of Aldrassil&d~
Sector   forest~
Desc     You have climbed into the dizzying heights of the great tree. The view
of the forest below is breathtaking. Tenaron Stormgrip meditates here,
watching over the balance of the glen.
~
#EXIT
Direction down~
ToRoom    26000
Desc      The base of the tree.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 26009 1 26005
  Reset E 1 26007 10 5
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     26006
Name     &dFel Rock - Entrance&d~
Sector   hills~
Desc     A dark, jagged cave entrance completely devoid of natural life. The earth
around it is stained a sickly purple and green. Vicious Grellkin guard
this corrupted cave.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    26007
Desc      The path back to the forest.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction down~
ToRoom    26011
Desc      The depths of Fel Rock.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 26003 2 26006
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     26007
Name     &MThe Path out of Shadowglen&d~
Sector   forest~
Desc     The main path leading out of the safety of the starting glen. The woods
become significantly more dangerous from here on out. To the west, a
corrupted cave radiates dark magic.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    26004
Desc      The western thicket.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    26009
Desc      The road to Dolanaar.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    26006
Desc      Fel Rock.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     26008
Name     &dShadowthread Cave&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     This cave is completely choked with thick, sticky spider webs. The bodies
of trapped animals hang from the ceiling. A terrifyingly large Giant
Webwood Spider claims this dark tunnel as her own.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    26002
Desc      The edge of the glen.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 26012 1 26008
  Reset E 1 26001 10 16
Reset M 0 26001 2 26008
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     26009
Name     &MThe Road to Dolanaar&d~
Sector   forest~
Desc     A wide, well-traveled dirt path. Night Elf sentinels patrol this route,
keeping it clear of aggressive wildlife. To the south, the once-peaceful
Starbreeze Village has fallen strangely quiet.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    26007
Desc      The path back to Shadowglen.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    26012
Desc      Continuing toward the town.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    26010
Desc      Starbreeze Village.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     26010
Name     &MStarbreeze Village - Outskirts&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     The beautiful, open-air buildings of the Night Elves have been violently
ransacked here. The Gnarlpine furbolgs, driven mad by an unseen corruption,
have violently taken over the town.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    26009
Desc      The main road.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    26021
Desc      The center of the ruined village.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 26007 2 26010
  Reset G 1 26005 10
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     26011
Name     &dFel Rock - Depths&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     The air is suffocatingly foul. Fel magic seeps from the very stone,
corrupting the earth and twisting the local grells into aggressive monsters.
~
#EXIT
Direction up~
ToRoom    26006
Desc      The cave entrance.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 26003 3 26011
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     26012
Name     &MDolanaar Approach&d~
Sector   forest~
Desc     The forest opens up into a large, beautiful clearing. Ahead, built into
the massive roots and branches of the world tree, is the bustling Night
Elf town of Dolanaar.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    26009
Desc      The main road.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    26013
Desc      The gates of Dolanaar.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 26010 1 26012
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     26013
Name     &MDolanaar - Gates&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     The entrance to the primary settlement outside of Darnassus. Sentinels
stand tall here, gripping their moonblades. The town is a haven for
travelers and a bastion against the creeping corruption.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    26012
Desc      The approach.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    26014
Desc      The center of town.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 26010 2 26013
  Reset E 1 26006 10 16
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     26014
Name     &MDolanaar - Center&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     A lively hub of commerce and rest. An inn provides shelter to weary
adventurers, while merchants trade goods beneath the glowing leaves. The
air smells of sweet apples and clean rain.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    26013
Desc      The gates.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    26015
Desc      The Moonwell.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    26018
Desc      The road deeper into Teldrassil.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset O 0 26008 3 26014
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     26015
Name     &CThe Dolanaar Moonwell&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     A beautiful, shallow pool of glowing silver water. This is a Moonwell,
a sacred fount of magical and physical healing blessed by Elune. Priestesses
tend to the waters day and night.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    26014
Desc      The center of town.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 26011 2 26015
Reset O 0 26009 2 26015
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     26016
Name     &dBan'ethil Barrow Den - Entrance&d~
Sector   hills~
Desc     A massive, earthen archway leads deep underground. These ancient barrow
dens are where the druids of the claw sleep their long slumbers, but
something has gone terribly wrong inside.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    26018
Desc      The main road.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction down~
ToRoom    26017
Desc      Descend into the dens.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 26006 2 26016
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     26017
Name     &dBan'ethil Barrow Den - Depths&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     The sleeping chambers are completely overrun by dark magic and corrupted
timberlings. The druids trapped inside are suffering from a terrible
nightmare.
~
#EXIT
Direction up~
ToRoom    26016
Desc      The entrance.
~
